The paper discusses the use of deep neural network ensembles for improving prediction performance and robustness against deception. This topic is highly relevant to the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). Additionally, the use of ensemble learning techniques is also relevant to the field of neural networks (cs.NE).
